popid_1939583883X="<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">DevMan provides batch processing - where a series of tasks can be run with little or no manual intervention.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">There are a number of jobs that although often simple may need to be done perhaps hundreds of times.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">For example printing a batch of thank you letters or tax certificates. <\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">At other times a number of records may need to have a status or flag changed.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">All input data is preselected via the standard filters (basic or advanced).<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">Batch processing has these benefits:<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 0; padding-left: 13px; margin-left: 0;\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\" style=\"font-family: Arial,\'Lucida Sans Unicode\',\'Lucida Grande\',\'Lucida Sans\';display:inline-block;width:13px;margin-left:-13px\">&#8226;<\/span><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">The job can be run at a time when the computing resources are less busy.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 0; padding-left: 13px; margin-left: 0;\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\" style=\"font-family: Arial,\'Lucida Sans Unicode\',\'Lucida Grande\',\'Lucida Sans\';display:inline-block;width:13px;margin-left:-13px\">&#8226;<\/span><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">The computing resources are not left idled with manual intervention and supervision.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 0; padding-left: 13px; margin-left: 0;\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\" style=\"font-family: Arial,\'Lucida Sans Unicode\',\'Lucida Grande\',\'Lucida Sans\';display:inline-block;width:13px;margin-left:-13px\">&#8226;<\/span><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">It allows the system to use different priorities for interactive and non-interactive work.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n\r"
popid_586296982="<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">Sum of money made available upon the donor\'s death.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">Bequest income, also know as legacy income, holds potential for any nonprofit.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">Although many bequests come from people with which there is no previous association, it makes sense to put effort into bequest marketing.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n\r"
popid_48442844X="<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">A method or technique that when followed is for the most part advantageous.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">Some organisations specialize in developing best practices but often these are developed from experience.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">In the case of DevMan, these may be recommendations based on the developers\' knowledge of the software.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">They also glean experience and ideas from DevMan\'s diverse client base and their experience with DevMan.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n\r"
