popid_961498996="<p><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">Breadcrumbs provide a trail of where you have been through the system.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">This allows you to specifically select a page that you had open earlier.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">Hover the cursor over the breadcrumb to check where it will take you<\/span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',Times,Georgia,serif;\">.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n\r"
popid_1804213861X="<p class=\"p_Normal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Internet Explorer<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_Normal\">&nbsp;<\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">Microsoft is withdrawing support for the original Internet Explorer (IE) browser, and will be focusing their efforts on a modern browsing experience such as the new Microsoft Edge.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">As IE is no longer supported by Microsoft, it will not receive security patches and updates. This puts your organization at risk.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">With this in mind, DevMan is maintaining pace with Microsoft and has also withdrawn support for the original IE browser.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">Therefore it is important to migrate your DevMan users onto a more modern browser, such as the new Microsoft Edge, Mozilla Firefox or Google Chrome.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">This will allow DevMan to run correctly and perform efficiently.<\/span><\/p>\n\r"
popid_1730617134X="<p class=\"p_Normal\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">A total sum of money that has been set aside for a specific purpose e.g. a CSI budget. <\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_Normal\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">This budget can be broken down and allocated to different departments, regions e.g. KwaZulu Natal or focus areas e.g. education. &nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_Normal\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">A budget is for a given period of time, usually one year. &nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n\r"
