popid_354461883="<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">Email sent to 6 or more recipients. Applies to most of what we would typically think of as bulk marketing.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">These emails go to a subscription list or a segment of your list. They can be used for events, promotions, newsletters, greetings etc.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">Bulk emails are subject to POPI, so will be sent to a subscription list of people who have granted permission to receive these emails, and include an unsubscribe link on each email.<\/span><\/p>\n\r"
