popid_555524665="<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">A fundraising initiative, perhaps an activity such as an event or mailshot.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">Its purpose is to raise funds for a specific project, e.g. constructing a building, undertaking a major building renovation or expansion, or purchasing a piece of necessary equipment.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">It can also be a move to renew lapsed donors or infrequent donors to give monthly.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\" style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Capital campaign<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">This is a one-off intensive drive for a something specific - perhaps a building, classroom, a bus or other motor-vehicle<\/span><\/p>\n\r"
