popid_222534125X="<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">These are the people, organisations and households you deal with - your clients, donors, prospects, grantees, volunteers.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">&nbsp;<\/span><br \/>\n\r<span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">Fundraising - these are prospects or donors. <\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">At a tertiary organisation these may be faculties, colleges, departments and units linked hierarchically.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">Grantmaking - &nbsp;grantees, primary contact, board member, administrative, finance or other personnel.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">DevMan allows any number of contacts. These may be linked to other contacts and you can categorize them in several ways. <\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">For example you may link employees and proposals to a recipient organisation.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent2\"><img alt=\"ContactHierarchy\" width=\"324\" height=\"252\" style=\"margin:0;width:324px;height:252px;border:none\" src=\"contacthierarchy.png\"\/><\/p>\n\r"
popid_2030068461="<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">Contacts may be linked to other contacts.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">Organisations will usually have a primary contact and other contact persons.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">They can be linked to other organisations as a co-funder or subsidiary<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n\r<div style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 0; line-height: 1.38; padding: 0 0 0 0; margin: 0 0 0 0;\"><table style=\"border:none; border-spacing:0;\">\n\r<tr>\n\r<td style=\"vertical-align:top; width:435px; padding:0; border:none\"><p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><img alt=\"ContactHierarchy\" width=\"324\" height=\"252\" style=\"margin:0;width:324px;height:252px;border:none\" src=\"contacthierarchy.png\"\/><\/p>\n\r<\/td>\n\r<td style=\"vertical-align:top; width:418px; padding:0; border:none\"><p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><img alt=\"HouseholdHierarchy\" width=\"322\" height=\"339\" style=\"margin:0;width:322px;height:339px;border:none\" src=\"householdhierarchy.png\"\/><\/p>\n\r<\/td>\n\r<\/tr>\n\r<\/table>\n\r<\/div>\n\r<p class=\"p_Normal\">&nbsp;<\/p>\n\r"
