popid_394768455X="<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">In fundraising, it\'s about engaging with prospect to build a relationship and preparing to ask.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">In doing this you need to keep them informed about your projects and build a desire to give<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n\r"
popid_1266041097="<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">To alter or otherwise personalise to suit individual requirements or specifications.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">Generally this is done by developing custom code to change functionality.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">Customization is often complex and it may incur more cost than configuration.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">Look up configure to see what this means and it\'s other benefits.<\/span><\/p>\n\r"
popid_2108279327="<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Centralise vital information<\/span><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\"> - Critical data is brought to the surface. Instead of flipping through pages, everyone will be on the same page.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Data visualization<\/span><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\"> - The visual representation helps you interpret your data and track performance metrics, enabling intuitive decision making. <\/span><\/p>\n\r"
