popid_1216143222X="<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">Financial transactions (donations from donors or payments to grantees) are batched and sent to Pastel as delimited files where they are imported via the Pastel import interface. <\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">Financial transactions in DevMan are linked to projects. Projects can be set up with one or more general ledger (GL) accounts and contra-accounts. <\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">When a donation or payment is entered in DevMan, they are allocated to a project and to one of the linked GL codes and contra-accounts associated with the project. <\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">This single point of entry reduces errors and increases productivity. <\/span><\/p>\n\r"
