popid_591635491="<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">Organisation is a type of contact. <\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">In fundraising these are your donors and prospects<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">In grantmaking, these are grantees - the companies you give money or services<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">To make it easy to find them add their Acronym or make your own acronym of three or more letters.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">Organisations are usually linked to other contacts including the primary contact person.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n\r<div style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 0; line-height: 1.38; padding: 0 0 0 0; margin: 0 0 0 0;\"><table style=\"border:none; border-spacing:0;\">\n\r<tr>\n\r<td style=\"vertical-align:top; width:435px; padding:0; border:none\"><p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\"><img alt=\"ContactHierarchy\" width=\"324\" height=\"252\" style=\"margin:0;width:324px;height:252px;border:none\" src=\"contacthierarchy.png\"\/><\/p>\n\r<\/td>\n\r<td style=\"vertical-align:top; width:418px; padding:0; border:none\"><p class=\"p_Normal\"><img alt=\"HouseholdHierarchy\" width=\"322\" height=\"339\" style=\"margin:0;width:322px;height:339px;border:none\" src=\"householdhierarchy.png\"\/><\/p>\n\r<\/td>\n\r<\/tr>\n\r<\/table>\n\r<\/div>\n\r<p class=\"p_Normal\">&nbsp;<\/p>\n\r"
popid_333452220="<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">The first level of protection to your data in DevMan is to logon with a user-id and password.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">It is therefore vital to use strong (complex) passwords and not to share it with anyone else.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">Within DevMan passwords are stored as encrypted values<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\" style=\"text-indent: 0; padding-left: 13px; margin-left: 38px;\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\" style=\"display:inline-block;width:13px;margin-left:-13px\">-<\/span><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">Password should be at least 8 characters long<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\" style=\"text-indent: 0; padding-left: 13px; margin-left: 38px;\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\" style=\"display:inline-block;width:13px;margin-left:-13px\">-<\/span><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">Use a variety of letters of the alphabet, numeric digits and special characters such as @, #, \$, %<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\" style=\"text-indent: 0; padding-left: 13px; margin-left: 38px;\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\" style=\"display:inline-block;width:13px;margin-left:-13px\">-<\/span><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">Use both upper-case and lower-case letters<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\" style=\"text-indent: 0; padding-left: 13px; margin-left: 38px;\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\" style=\"display:inline-block;width:13px;margin-left:-13px\">-<\/span><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">Make up a pass phrase as a password reminder that makes sense to you only.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\" style=\"text-indent: 0; padding-left: 13px; margin-left: 38px;\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\" style=\"display:inline-block;width:13px;margin-left:-13px\">-<\/span><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">Do not use part of your ID, driver’s license number and personal facts about you in the password.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; color: #000000;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n\r"
