popid_406207810="<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">Projects are core in fundraising (IA) &nbsp;and grantmaking.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">You have agreed to grant or raise funds for a project (a planned undertaking, a task &nbsp;or problem such as HIV\/Aids project or poverty alleviation project). <\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">Projects go through a life cycle, typically from \'proposal request\' through to \'approved’ to ‘closed’. <\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">Additional things are recorded about projects:<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">Payments – one or more payments can be made toward a project<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">Progress reports – you request progress reports for a project<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">Fundraisers may not be concerned with having many projects or perhaps you receive a large number of general donations to be used at your discretion.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">In either case, we suggest you create a project called General Donations or something similar (perhaps include the year)<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">, and allocate your general pledges and donations to this project.<\/span><\/p>\n\r"
popid_659924695="<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\" style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">The donor<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">Have a clear understanding of what the donor\'s goals are. Is your overall agenda in line with theirs.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\" style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">The recipient - You<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">You need to be very clear in your mind, so you can articulate who you are and &nbsp;give a credible picture.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\" style=\"text-indent: 0; padding-left: 13px; margin-left: 38px;\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\" style=\"font-family: Arial,\'Lucida Sans Unicode\',\'Lucida Grande\',\'Lucida Sans\';display:inline-block;width:13px;margin-left:-13px\">&#8226;<\/span><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">Who are you, and what is your identity?<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\" style=\"text-indent: 0; padding-left: 13px; margin-left: 38px;\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\" style=\"font-family: Arial,\'Lucida Sans Unicode\',\'Lucida Grande\',\'Lucida Sans\';display:inline-block;width:13px;margin-left:-13px\">&#8226;<\/span><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">SWOT What are your Strengths and Weaknesses, and what Opportunities and Threats confront you?<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\" style=\"text-indent: 0; padding-left: 13px; margin-left: 38px;\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\" style=\"font-family: Arial,\'Lucida Sans Unicode\',\'Lucida Grande\',\'Lucida Sans\';display:inline-block;width:13px;margin-left:-13px\">&#8226;<\/span><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">What is your track record?<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\" style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Specific project<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">Not merely to raise money<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">Link your mission\/strategy with the specific project. <\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">The projects you plan should be part of your strategy<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\" style=\"text-indent: 0; padding-left: 13px; margin-left: 38px;\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\" style=\"font-family: Arial,\'Lucida Sans Unicode\',\'Lucida Grande\',\'Lucida Sans\';display:inline-block;width:13px;margin-left:-13px\">&#8226;<\/span><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">Know your objectives.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\" style=\"text-indent: 0; padding-left: 13px; margin-left: 38px;\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\" style=\"font-family: Arial,\'Lucida Sans Unicode\',\'Lucida Grande\',\'Lucida Sans\';display:inline-block;width:13px;margin-left:-13px\">&#8226;<\/span><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">What you want to achieve (your ends)<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\" style=\"text-indent: 0; padding-left: 13px; margin-left: 38px;\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\" style=\"font-family: Arial,\'Lucida Sans Unicode\',\'Lucida Grande\',\'Lucida Sans\';display:inline-block;width:13px;margin-left:-13px\">&#8226;<\/span><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">How you want to achieve it (your means)<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\" style=\"text-indent: 0; padding-left: 13px; margin-left: 38px;\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\" style=\"font-family: Arial,\'Lucida Sans Unicode\',\'Lucida Grande\',\'Lucida Sans\';display:inline-block;width:13px;margin-left:-13px\">&#8226;<\/span><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">Who the main beneficiaries will be.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\" style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Presentation<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">Know the Process.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">How you are going to achieve the project purpose?<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">People identify with people. Give your proposal a human quality, not just a dry summary.<\/span><\/p>\n\r"
