popid_567786573="<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">Once you\'ve selected the information you want to report you have styles and layouts to choose from.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">Styles:<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 0; padding-left: 13px; margin-left: 0;\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\" style=\"font-family: Arial,\'Lucida Sans Unicode\',\'Lucida Grande\',\'Lucida Sans\';display:inline-block;width:13px;margin-left:-13px\">&#8226;<\/span><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">High level summaries and graphs (statistical) <\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 0; padding-left: 13px; margin-left: 0;\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\" style=\"font-family: Arial,\'Lucida Sans Unicode\',\'Lucida Grande\',\'Lucida Sans\';display:inline-block;width:13px;margin-left:-13px\">&#8226;<\/span><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">Displayed by up to three levels<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 0; padding-left: 13px; margin-left: 0;\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\" style=\"font-family: Arial,\'Lucida Sans Unicode\',\'Lucida Grande\',\'Lucida Sans\';display:inline-block;width:13px;margin-left:-13px\">&#8226;<\/span><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">Presented in columns (Lists)<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 0; padding-left: 13px; margin-left: 0;\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\" style=\"font-family: Arial,\'Lucida Sans Unicode\',\'Lucida Grande\',\'Lucida Sans\';display:inline-block;width:13px;margin-left:-13px\">&#8226;<\/span><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">Name list<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 0; padding-left: 13px; margin-left: 0;\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\" style=\"font-family: Arial,\'Lucida Sans Unicode\',\'Lucida Grande\',\'Lucida Sans\';display:inline-block;width:13px;margin-left:-13px\">&#8226;<\/span><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">Address list<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 0; padding-left: 13px; margin-left: 0;\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\" style=\"font-family: Arial,\'Lucida Sans Unicode\',\'Lucida Grande\',\'Lucida Sans\';display:inline-block;width:13px;margin-left:-13px\">&#8226;<\/span><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">Address list with mailing status<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 0; padding-left: 13px; margin-left: 0;\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\" style=\"font-family: Arial,\'Lucida Sans Unicode\',\'Lucida Grande\',\'Lucida Sans\';display:inline-block;width:13px;margin-left:-13px\">&#8226;<\/span><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">Telephone directory<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 0; padding-left: 13px; margin-left: 0;\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\" style=\"font-family: Arial,\'Lucida Sans Unicode\',\'Lucida Grande\',\'Lucida Sans\';display:inline-block;width:13px;margin-left:-13px\">&#8226;<\/span><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">Detailed list<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 0; padding-left: 13px; margin-left: 0;\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\" style=\"font-family: Arial,\'Lucida Sans Unicode\',\'Lucida Grande\',\'Lucida Sans\';display:inline-block;width:13px;margin-left:-13px\">&#8226;<\/span><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">Detailed list - update details<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 0; padding-left: 13px; margin-left: 0;\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\" style=\"font-family: Arial,\'Lucida Sans Unicode\',\'Lucida Grande\',\'Lucida Sans\';display:inline-block;width:13px;margin-left:-13px\">&#8226;<\/span><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">Detailed list - with birth dates<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 0; padding-left: 13px; margin-left: 0;\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\" style=\"font-family: Arial,\'Lucida Sans Unicode\',\'Lucida Grande\',\'Lucida Sans\';display:inline-block;width:13px;margin-left:-13px\">&#8226;<\/span><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">Detailed list - prospect tracking<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 0; padding-left: 13px; margin-left: 0;\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\" style=\"font-family: Arial,\'Lucida Sans Unicode\',\'Lucida Grande\',\'Lucida Sans\';display:inline-block;width:13px;margin-left:-13px\">&#8226;<\/span><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">Donor list - standard (total amount for all years)<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 0; padding-left: 13px; margin-left: 0;\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\" style=\"font-family: Arial,\'Lucida Sans Unicode\',\'Lucida Grande\',\'Lucida Sans\';display:inline-block;width:13px;margin-left:-13px\">&#8226;<\/span><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">Donor list - standard (total amount only)<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 0; padding-left: 13px; margin-left: 0;\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\" style=\"font-family: Arial,\'Lucida Sans Unicode\',\'Lucida Grande\',\'Lucida Sans\';display:inline-block;width:13px;margin-left:-13px\">&#8226;<\/span><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">Donor list - detailed<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 0; padding-left: 13px; margin-left: 0;\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\" style=\"font-family: Arial,\'Lucida Sans Unicode\',\'Lucida Grande\',\'Lucida Sans\';display:inline-block;width:13px;margin-left:-13px\">&#8226;<\/span><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">Donor list - with project detail<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 0; padding-left: 13px; margin-left: 0;\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\" style=\"font-family: Arial,\'Lucida Sans Unicode\',\'Lucida Grande\',\'Lucida Sans\';display:inline-block;width:13px;margin-left:-13px\">&#8226;<\/span><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">5 year donation summary<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 0; padding-left: 13px; margin-left: 0;\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\" style=\"font-family: Arial,\'Lucida Sans Unicode\',\'Lucida Grande\',\'Lucida Sans\';display:inline-block;width:13px;margin-left:-13px\">&#8226;<\/span><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">Qualification list<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n\r"
popid_355722895="<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">An assigned role allows a user to access the information they need to have access to.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">These roles can be cared for by one person or assigned to different persons.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">Examples of roles: Administrator, project officer, finance clerk, fundraiser, researcher, director.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p style=\"line-height: 1.28; margin: 0 0 11px 0;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; color: #000000;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n\r"
popid_1330712592="<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">Role-based access or role-based permissions add a layer of grouping above user-based access i.e. supersedes user-based access at an individual level.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">Users still have a log-in name and password, but role-based access allows users to be assigned to groups and in turn are assigned specific capabilities.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">Examples of common groups include managers, system administrators and users.<\/span><\/p>\n\r"
popid_355776531="<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">A salt is random data used as an additional input to a function that hashes a password to improve defense against attacks.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">For each new password a random new salt is generated, typically concatenated and processed in a special function. <\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">This is stored in the databases instead of the original password.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n\r"
