popid_1654300138="<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">Many not-for-profit organisations may enjoy preferential tax treatment if granted approval as a Public Benefit Organisation (PBO).<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">Approved PBOs have the privilege and responsibility of using donations or grants on a tax-free basis. <\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">The South African Government has provided a tax deduction for certain donations made by taxpayers.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">A taxpayer making a bona fide donation in cash or of property in kind to a section 18A-approved organisation, is entitled to a deduction from taxable income if the donation is supported by the necessary section 18A receipt issued by the organisation or, in certain circumstances, by an employees’ tax certificate reflecting the donations made by the employee. The amount of donations which may qualify for a tax deduction is limited.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">For more details go to: http:\/\/www.sars.gov.za<\/span>\/ClientSegments\/Businesses\/TEO\/Pages\/default.aspx<\/p>\n\r"
popid_396388257X="<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">Templates are a common feature of many software applications. For example many cell phone users are familiar with text templates as are Word and &nbsp;Excel users.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">Simply put &nbsp;a template is a pre-formatted file type that can be used (and re-used) to quickly create a specific file. <\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">In the template, everything such as Font, Size, Colour, Background pictures are pre-formatted but users can also edit them<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">In DevMan we take advantage of this useful feature and employ this technique for communications (including sms, email and letters to post) and HTML. <\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n\r"
