popid_1283593846="<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">Re-usable predefined and well-formed* snippets or pieces of HTML &nbsp;that can be inserted into an HTML document or template.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">Content writers can select a template from a list by clicking the button in the toolbar. <\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">Using this feature, the user does not need to start formatting the text from scratch and does not need to have HTML experience. <\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">Designers can prepare well designed templates which helps avoid user errors before they happen. <\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">*Well formed means it meets the criteria for HTML processors to read the fragment.<\/span><\/p>\n\r"
