popid_262574434="<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">What to expect from the system?<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">Manage contacts and group them, capture donations, add payments, send out mailshots, integrate with other<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">Will you want to manage projects, and approaches.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">What Can I do with Devman?<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\" style=\"text-indent: 0; padding-left: 13px; margin-left: 38px;\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\" style=\"font-family: Arial,\'Lucida Sans Unicode\',\'Lucida Grande\',\'Lucida Sans\';display:inline-block;width:13px;margin-left:-13px\">&#8226;<\/span><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">Find and call<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\" style=\"text-indent: 0; padding-left: 13px; margin-left: 38px;\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\" style=\"font-family: Arial,\'Lucida Sans Unicode\',\'Lucida Grande\',\'Lucida Sans\';display:inline-block;width:13px;margin-left:-13px\">&#8226;<\/span><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">Classify and report by flags<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\" style=\"text-indent: 0; padding-left: 13px; margin-left: 38px;\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\" style=\"font-family: Arial,\'Lucida Sans Unicode\',\'Lucida Grande\',\'Lucida Sans\';display:inline-block;width:13px;margin-left:-13px\">&#8226;<\/span><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">Email\/SMS <\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\" style=\"text-indent: 0; padding-left: 13px; margin-left: 38px;\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\" style=\"font-family: Arial,\'Lucida Sans Unicode\',\'Lucida Grande\',\'Lucida Sans\';display:inline-block;width:13px;margin-left:-13px\">&#8226;<\/span><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">Mailshot<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\" style=\"text-indent: 0; padding-left: 13px; margin-left: 38px;\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\" style=\"font-family: Arial,\'Lucida Sans Unicode\',\'Lucida Grande\',\'Lucida Sans\';display:inline-block;width:13px;margin-left:-13px\">&#8226;<\/span><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">Newsletters<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\" style=\"text-indent: 0; padding-left: 13px; margin-left: 38px;\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\" style=\"font-family: Arial,\'Lucida Sans Unicode\',\'Lucida Grande\',\'Lucida Sans\';display:inline-block;width:13px;margin-left:-13px\">&#8226;<\/span><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">Record payments and send tax certificates<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\" style=\"text-indent: 0; padding-left: 13px; margin-left: 38px;\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\" style=\"font-family: Arial,\'Lucida Sans Unicode\',\'Lucida Grande\',\'Lucida Sans\';display:inline-block;width:13px;margin-left:-13px\">&#8226;<\/span><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">Acknowledgment &nbsp;and other letters<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\" style=\"text-indent: 0; padding-left: 13px; margin-left: 38px;\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\" style=\"font-family: Arial,\'Lucida Sans Unicode\',\'Lucida Grande\',\'Lucida Sans\';display:inline-block;width:13px;margin-left:-13px\">&#8226;<\/span><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">Donations &nbsp;<\/span><\/p>"
popid_2009908456X="<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">Applies to anything that isn’t bulk i.e. 5 or less recipients. It is a response to a user’s action, or in some cases, their lack of action.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">Transactional emails are often the first step to start communications with your recipients.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">For example, you send an email to welcome your new donor. Transactional emails refer to automatic, triggered, personalized and one-to-one email. <\/span><\/p>\n\r"
