popid_1477728816X="<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Workflow<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">Workflow is the series of activities (steps) to see a work process (business process) through from initiation to completion.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">Moving from one step to another depends on the results of a previous step.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">It is often limited to simple ideas such as: Stop if a task fails or carry on if the task succeeds.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">Often you need more comprehensive logic such as executing one of a number of steps depending on some action or event.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">Controlling what is executed depending on something more than a previous task’s success or failure can be described as conditional workflow.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">Workflows can be as simple or as complex as your business processes require. They can be started by a user, or initiated automatically based on an event (created or changed).<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">DevMan<\/span><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\"> can be modified to cater for your organization\'s own workflow preference.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">Here are some examples of workflow that may be used in CSI and CRM projects.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">CSI - Proposal\/Project<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">You receive requests for funding daily. You must decide whether to decline or accept the request. <\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">Thus your proposals go through a workflow or life cycle.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">Here is a an example of a simple grantmaking workflow:<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent2\" style=\"text-indent: 0; padding-left: 13px; margin-left: 77px;\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent2\" style=\"font-family: Arial,\'Lucida Sans Unicode\',\'Lucida Grande\',\'Lucida Sans\';display:inline-block;width:13px;margin-left:-13px\">&#8226;<\/span><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent2\">new proposal<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent2\" style=\"text-indent: 0; padding-left: 13px; margin-left: 77px;\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent2\" style=\"font-family: Arial,\'Lucida Sans Unicode\',\'Lucida Grande\',\'Lucida Sans\';display:inline-block;width:13px;margin-left:-13px\">&#8226;<\/span><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent2\">under consideration<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent2\" style=\"text-indent: 0; padding-left: 13px; margin-left: 77px;\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent2\" style=\"font-family: Arial,\'Lucida Sans Unicode\',\'Lucida Grande\',\'Lucida Sans\';display:inline-block;width:13px;margin-left:-13px\">&#8226;<\/span><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent2\">declined<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent2\" style=\"text-indent: 0; padding-left: 13px; margin-left: 77px;\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent2\" style=\"font-family: Arial,\'Lucida Sans Unicode\',\'Lucida Grande\',\'Lucida Sans\';display:inline-block;width:13px;margin-left:-13px\">&#8226;<\/span><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent2\">approved <\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent2\" style=\"text-indent: 0; padding-left: 13px; margin-left: 77px;\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent2\" style=\"font-family: Arial,\'Lucida Sans Unicode\',\'Lucida Grande\',\'Lucida Sans\';display:inline-block;width:13px;margin-left:-13px\">&#8226;<\/span><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent2\">completed<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">CRM - Project<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">This is a typical workflow cycle for proposals:<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 0; padding-left: 90px; margin-left: 0;\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent2\" style=\"font-family: Arial,\'Lucida Sans Unicode\',\'Lucida Grande\',\'Lucida Sans\';display:inline-block;width:13px;margin-left:-13px\">&#8226;<\/span><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">in concept<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 0; padding-left: 90px; margin-left: 0;\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent2\" style=\"font-family: Arial,\'Lucida Sans Unicode\',\'Lucida Grande\',\'Lucida Sans\';display:inline-block;width:13px;margin-left:-13px\">&#8226;<\/span><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">decision pending<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 0; padding-left: 90px; margin-left: 0;\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent2\" style=\"font-family: Arial,\'Lucida Sans Unicode\',\'Lucida Grande\',\'Lucida Sans\';display:inline-block;width:13px;margin-left:-13px\">&#8226;<\/span><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">declined<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 0; padding-left: 90px; margin-left: 0;\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent2\" style=\"font-family: Arial,\'Lucida Sans Unicode\',\'Lucida Grande\',\'Lucida Sans\';display:inline-block;width:13px;margin-left:-13px\">&#8226;<\/span><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">approved <\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 0; padding-left: 90px; margin-left: 0;\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent2\" style=\"font-family: Arial,\'Lucida Sans Unicode\',\'Lucida Grande\',\'Lucida Sans\';display:inline-block;width:13px;margin-left:-13px\">&#8226;<\/span><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">under approach <\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 0; padding-left: 90px; margin-left: 0;\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent2\" style=\"font-family: Arial,\'Lucida Sans Unicode\',\'Lucida Grande\',\'Lucida Sans\';display:inline-block;width:13px;margin-left:-13px\">&#8226;<\/span><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">partially funded<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 0; padding-left: 90px; margin-left: 0;\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent2\" style=\"font-family: Arial,\'Lucida Sans Unicode\',\'Lucida Grande\',\'Lucida Sans\';display:inline-block;width:13px;margin-left:-13px\">&#8226;<\/span><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">fully funded<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 0; padding-left: 90px; margin-left: 0;\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent2\" style=\"font-family: Arial,\'Lucida Sans Unicode\',\'Lucida Grande\',\'Lucida Sans\';display:inline-block;width:13px;margin-left:-13px\">&#8226;<\/span><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">completed - closed<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 0; padding-left: 90px; margin-left: 0;\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent2\" style=\"font-family: Arial,\'Lucida Sans Unicode\',\'Lucida Grande\',\'Lucida Sans\';display:inline-block;width:13px;margin-left:-13px\">&#8226;<\/span><span class=\"f_KidzNormal\">completed - terminated<\/span><\/p>"
popid_1420286391="<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">When entering a project name avoid:<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent2\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent2\">Using the name of the organisation<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent2\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent2\">Copying the name of another project.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">You are strongly encouraged to give the project a name that clearly describes it.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">This will help you easily identify the project later on.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">Here\'s an example:<\/span><\/p>\n\r<div style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 0; line-height: 1.38; padding: 0 0 0 0; margin: 0 38px 0 38px;\"><table style=\"border:solid thin #800000; border-spacing:0;\" role=\"cell\">\n\r<tr>\n\r<td style=\"vertical-align:top; width:497px; padding:0; border:none\"><p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">Suppose an organisation has as its name: Skills Development Organisation<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">Their aim is to educate previously illiterate persons in essential life skills.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">You could give it a name that describes this purpose such as:<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\" style=\"margin: 0 38px 0 62px;\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">Life Skills Education for Adults<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\" style=\"margin: 0 38px 0 62px;\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\"> ... or ...<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\" style=\"margin: 0 38px 0 62px;\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">Life Skills for Formerly Illiterate Persons<\/span><\/p>\n\r<\/td>\n\r<\/tr>\n\r<\/table>\n\r<\/div>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n\r"
popid_1438550885="<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">Projects page<\/span><\/p>\n\r<div style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.38; padding: 0 0 0 0; margin: 0 38px 0 56px;\"><table style=\"border:none; border-spacing:0;\" role=\"cell\">\n\r<tr>\n\r<td style=\"vertical-align:top; padding:0; border:none\"><p class=\"p_Normal\">&nbsp;<\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\"><img alt=\"wpProjectSearch\" width=\"831\" height=\"268\" style=\"margin:0;width:831px;height:268px;border:none\" src=\"wpprojectsearch.png\"\/><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_Normal\">&nbsp;<\/p>\n\r<\/td>\n\r<\/tr>\n\r<\/table>\n\r<\/div>\n\r"
popid_105948682X="<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\" style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">The donor<\/span><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">. <\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">Have a clear understanding of what the donor\'s goals are. Is your overall agenda in line with theirs.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\" style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">The recipient - You<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">You need to be very clear in your mind, so you can articulate who you are and &nbsp;give a credible picture.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\" style=\"text-indent: 0; padding-left: 13px; margin-left: 38px;\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\" style=\"font-family: Arial,\'Lucida Sans Unicode\',\'Lucida Grande\',\'Lucida Sans\';display:inline-block;width:13px;margin-left:-13px\">&#8226;<\/span><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">Who are you, and what is your identity?<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\" style=\"text-indent: 0; padding-left: 13px; margin-left: 38px;\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\" style=\"font-family: Arial,\'Lucida Sans Unicode\',\'Lucida Grande\',\'Lucida Sans\';display:inline-block;width:13px;margin-left:-13px\">&#8226;<\/span><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">SWOT What are your Strengths and Weaknesses, and what Opportunities and Threats confront you?<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\" style=\"text-indent: 0; padding-left: 13px; margin-left: 38px;\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\" style=\"font-family: Arial,\'Lucida Sans Unicode\',\'Lucida Grande\',\'Lucida Sans\';display:inline-block;width:13px;margin-left:-13px\">&#8226;<\/span><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">What is your track record?<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\" style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Specific project<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">Not merely to raise money<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">Link your mission\/strategy with the specific project. <\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">The projects you plan should be part of your strategy<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\" style=\"text-indent: 0; padding-left: 13px; margin-left: 38px;\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\" style=\"font-family: Arial,\'Lucida Sans Unicode\',\'Lucida Grande\',\'Lucida Sans\';display:inline-block;width:13px;margin-left:-13px\">&#8226;<\/span><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">Know your objectives.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\" style=\"text-indent: 0; padding-left: 13px; margin-left: 38px;\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\" style=\"font-family: Arial,\'Lucida Sans Unicode\',\'Lucida Grande\',\'Lucida Sans\';display:inline-block;width:13px;margin-left:-13px\">&#8226;<\/span><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">What you want to achieve (your ends)<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\" style=\"text-indent: 0; padding-left: 13px; margin-left: 38px;\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\" style=\"font-family: Arial,\'Lucida Sans Unicode\',\'Lucida Grande\',\'Lucida Sans\';display:inline-block;width:13px;margin-left:-13px\">&#8226;<\/span><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">How you want to achieve it (your means)<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\" style=\"text-indent: 0; padding-left: 13px; margin-left: 38px;\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\" style=\"font-family: Arial,\'Lucida Sans Unicode\',\'Lucida Grande\',\'Lucida Sans\';display:inline-block;width:13px;margin-left:-13px\">&#8226;<\/span><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">Who the main beneficiaries will be.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\" style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Presentation<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">Know the Process.<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">How you are going to achieve the project purpose?<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">People identify with people. Give your proposal a human quality, not just a dry summary.<\/span><\/p>\n\r"
popid_2069118602="<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">If you\'ve lost your Devman shortcut and need help to do this again follow these steps:<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">Changer the URL shown here by replacing &quot;YourCompanyName&quot; withmatch your company\'s Devman address: <\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">&nbsp;<\/span><br \/>\n\r<span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">http:\/\/YourCompanyName.kidzafrica.co.za\/KidzNet\/Codelib\/General\/Login.aspx?UserID=YourName<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">To create a shortcut on your desktop<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">Go to a clear space on the desktop <\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">Right-click and &quot;new shortcut&quot; and copy the url as example above and go &quot;next&quot; and name it “Devman” and Finish<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n\r<p class=\"p_KidzNormalIndent\"><span class=\"f_KidzNormalIndent\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n\r"
